-----------------------------------------------------------------------
-                          QUICK REFERENCES                           -
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

new session => tmux new -s work
reattach session => tmux a -d

create window  => C-a c
close window   => C-d
list windows   => C-a w
rename current window => C-a ,
close session => C-a & or C-a :kill-session

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
-                          OTHER OPERATIONS                           -
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1. copy txt from a pane to vim in a different pane
 * Ctrl + A [ to enter copy mode
 * Move to start of txt
 * Hit space
 * select region, hit enter to end (and copy)
 * go back to vim, enter insert mode
 * Ctrl + A ] to paste
2. common copy mode shortcuts
 * Begin of line ^
 * End of line   $
 * Page down     Ctrl-d
 * Page up       Ctrl-u
